# 🚦 Health Check Service

A FastAPI microservice for managing service health statuses.

## 🌐 Features

- View, add, update, and delete service health.
- Simple in-memory data store.

## ▶️ Run Locally

```bash
git clone https://github.com/bzaypandey/health-check-service.git
cd health-check-service
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
